---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { SITE } from "../site-config";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="sr-only">
      Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName}, an AI Engineer and Computer Science student specializing in deep learning, computer vision, and building intelligent automation systems.
    </p>
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="text-sm font-light flex flex-col gap-1">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName}, an AI Engineer based in {SITE.location.countryName}, specializing in training deep neural architectures and deploying interpretability frameworks.
      </p>
      
      <p class="font-medium text-white mt-1">Core Tech Stack:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-xs grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-2 gap-y-0.5">
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>PyTorch & TF</li>
        <li>Computer Vision</li>
        <li>XGBoost / SHAP</li>
        <li>n8n Automation</li>
        <li>Machine Learning</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="text-xs font-light flex flex-col gap-1 mt-1 border-t border-neutral-800 pt-2">
      <p class="font-medium text-white text-sm">Key Engineering Projects:</p>
      <p>• <strong>EduAgent:</strong> YouTube RAG pipeline using Llama for study assistance.</p>
      <p>• <strong>CropDoc:</strong> Custom CNN for betel leaf crop disease classification.</p>
      <p>• <strong>Explainable AI:</strong> Heart disease diagnostics using XGBoost and SHAP/LIME.</p>
      <p>• <strong>Affective Recs:</strong> Real-time music/movie recommendation engines via DeepFace.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Card>